# Git LFS tracking rules for binary demo deliverables
# (see docs/demo/README.md for context)

# Demo PPT — large binary, prefer LFS
*.pptx filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text

# Demo video — only commit if < 50MB; metadata in demo-recording.md
# NOTE: large videos should be excluded from git via .gitignore, not LFS-tracked
# (LFS still bloats LFS storage, and the plan explicitly says: > 50MB → not in Git)

# Screenshots are small (< 5MB each); keep in git as-is, no LFS
